Osas Ighodaro (onye amụrụ Osariemen Martha Elizabeth Ighodaro ; 26 Ọktoba n'afọ 1983) bụ Nigerian American  , onye na-emepụta ihe nkiri, onye na-eme ihe nkiri na onye ọrụ ebere
O meriri na asụm mpi Miss Black USA Pageant   n' afọ 2010 ma wee hibe The Joyful Joy Foundation, iji chụ nta  ego ma gbasa ozi iji buso oria iba bụ Malaria agha
Na mgbakwunye, ọso nwe mee 2014 Africa Magic Viewers Choice Awards
Ọ rụrụ ọrụ nke  dika Adanna(Danni) n'ihe nkiri Tinsel , wee turu ugo dika onye kacha nwe mee ihe nkiri nke ELOY n'afọ 2014
Osas weputara ihe nkiri Nollywood kacha elu na n'afọ 2018
A mụrụ Ighodaro na Bronx, dí na New York, United States, nne na nna ya bụ ndị Nigeria si Edo State
O nwetara akara ugo mmụta mbụ ya na mgbasa ozi ma nwekwa mmụta n'agbambọ na Ama egwuregwu na  Pennsylvania State University-
Ọ nwetakwara akara ugo mmụta dị elu na ọrụ nka na Actors Studio Drama School at Pace University
Ọ kwagara Naịjirịa n’afọ 2012 ka ọ nanị ọnwa isii tupu Ọ  laghachi mba United States; mana o nwetara ọrụ ndị ọzọ, tinyere Tinsel  kpatara na Ọ   laghachighi kemgbe ahụ
Ọ kwadoro mmemme Maltina Dance All Reality
Ọ bụ onye guzobere Joyful Joy Foundation   ma bụrụ kwa onye otu Ụmụ nwanyi Alpha Kappa Alpha
Ya na Folu Storms sonyeere   MTV Shuga   maka ihe usoro nkiri nke anọ n'ọnwa nk'iri n'afọ 2019
Ọ lụrụ Gbenro Ajibade n'ọnwa Juun afọ 2015
Ha mụrụ nwa mbụ ha na afọ 2016
Ha gbara onwe ha alụkwaghịm ozigbo ozigbo
